title: Timeline incorrectly show most ops on gpu:0
body_html:
Timeline show most ops on gpu:0, which disagree with nvidia-smi and device placement log.

TF version v1.2.0-rc0-735-gf48673b (less than two weeks ago)

Attachments (remove txt suffix)
chrome___tracing.pdf
trace.json.txt
jupyter.log.txt
run_metadata.pb.txt
